# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Project runtime data — all operational dirs grouped under runtime/.
# Directory structure tracked via .gitkeep; contents not.
#
# Each runtime/<sub> has one purpose:
#   runtime/data/         — source data (rsync'd ShuttleSet, future OOD eval).
#   runtime/checkpoints/  — model weights, organised per-architecture
#                           (e.g. runtime/checkpoints/bric/, runtime/checkpoints/bst/,
#                            plus shared third-party caches like
#                            runtime/checkpoints/tracknetv3/, runtime/checkpoints/yolo11/).
#   runtime/experiments/  — training run manifests + metrics, organised per-architecture
#                           (e.g. runtime/experiments/bric/, runtime/experiments/bst/).
#   runtime/cache/        — derived computations (player tracks, etc.) — re-derivable,
#                           shared across architectures.
#   runtime/jobs/         — per-job inference artefacts (frame thumbnails, softmax).
#                           Persists for the lifetime of the corresponding jobs row in
#                           runtime/state/inference.db. v1 has no automatic TTL — files
#                           are removed when the job is explicitly deleted.
#   runtime/uploads/      — user-uploaded videos.
#   runtime/state/        — backend operational state (SQLite at inference.db).
#                           Distinct from runtime/cache/ — losing state/ wipes inference
#                           history but doesn't break training/serving. See docs/storage.md.
#
# Only BRIC's subdirs are pre-created below, since BRIC is the only
# architecture currently using this structure. BST or future architectures
# add their own subdirs following the same `runtime/<dir>/<arch>/*` + `.gitkeep`
# pattern.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

runtime/data/shuttleset/clips/*
!runtime/data/shuttleset/clips/.gitkeep
runtime/data/shuttleset/rally_clips/*
!runtime/data/shuttleset/rally_clips/.gitkeep
runtime/data/shuttleset/raw_video/*
!runtime/data/shuttleset/raw_video/.gitkeep

runtime/checkpoints/bric/*
!runtime/checkpoints/bric/.gitkeep
runtime/checkpoints/tracknetv3/*
!runtime/checkpoints/tracknetv3/.gitkeep
runtime/checkpoints/yolo11/*
!runtime/checkpoints/yolo11/.gitkeep

runtime/experiments/bric/*
!runtime/experiments/bric/.gitkeep

runtime/cache/players/*
!runtime/cache/players/.gitkeep
runtime/cache/shuttle/*
!runtime/cache/shuttle/.gitkeep
runtime/cache/rgb/*
!runtime/cache/rgb/.gitkeep
runtime/cache/validation/

runtime/jobs/*
!runtime/jobs/.gitkeep

runtime/uploads/*
!runtime/uploads/.gitkeep

runtime/state/*
!runtime/state/.gitkeep

# Ultralytics auto-downloads YOLO weights into the current working directory
# (or to ~/.cache/ultralytics/) on first use. Catch any that land in the repo root
# regardless. Production code should explicitly load from checkpoints/yolo11/.
yolo*.pt
*.engine

# Ultralytics training/predict default output dir
runs/
